## 📞 Quick Reference Commands

### Setup
```bash
sudo bash setup_testlab.sh
```

### Monitor Suricata
```bash
# All SQL injection alerts
tail -f /var/log/suricata/eve.json | jq 'select(.alert.signature_id >= 1000200)'

# Specific SID
tail -f /var/log/suricata/eve.json | jq 'select(.alert.signature_id == 1000200)'

# Count by type
jq -r '.alert.msg' /var/log/suricata/eve.json | sort | uniq -c
```

### Test Payload
```bash
curl -X POST http://testlab.local/test-lab/login_vulnerable.php \
  -d "username=admin' OR 1=1 --&password=test"
```

### Verify Setup
```bash
# Check database
mysql -u root -p testlab -e "SELECT COUNT(*) FROM users;"

# Check files
ls -la /var/www/html/test-lab/

# Check rules
grep "1000200\|1000201" /var/log/suricata/suricata.log
```

